



<div id="fileContents">
<h2>HIST 119: <strong>The Civil War and Reconstruction Era, 1845-1877 </strong></h2>
<table id="lectureHeader" summary="lecture header" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
	<tr>
		<td width="510" nowrap="nowrap">
			<span id="lectureNum">Lecture 9 - </span>
			<span id="lectureName">John Brown's Holy War: Terrorist or Heroic Revolutionary?</span></td>
		<td width="248" id="lectureNav" nowrap="nowrap">
			<span id="backNav"><a href="lecture08.html">&lt;&lt; previous session</a></span>
			<span id="navPipe">|</span>
